directives.name: IfBreakpointDirective
directives.description:
Structural directive that shows/hides element based on breakpoint config. Usage:

show on xs *ovIfBreakpoint="'xs'"

show on xs, sm and md *ovIfBreakpoint="'xs'; to: 'md'"

show on xs, sm and md else show another template *ovIfBreakpoint="'xs'; to: 'md'; else: otherRef;"
directives.rawdescription:
Structural directive that shows/hides element based on breakpoint config.
Usage:

*ovIfBreakpoint="'xs'"

show on xs, sm and md

show on xs, sm and md else show another template

components.name: ProductOutOfStockComponent
components.templateData:
<ov-product [product]="product">
  <section actions>
    <ov-button type="inverted">
      <ov-icon icon="envelope" color="primary" size="xs"></ov-icon>
      Contact
    </ov-button>
  </section>
  <section footer>
    <ov-message type="error">This product is out of stock</ov-message>
  </section>
</ov-product>

components.name: ProductReplacedComponent
components.templateData:
<section>
  <ov-title class="old-title">{{ product.title }}</ov-title>
  <ov-message type="warn">is replaced by: </ov-message>
  <ov-title>{{ product.replacement.title }}</ov-title>
  <ov-button>Checkout replacement</ov-button>
</section>

setSignature.name: input
setSignature.rawdescription: The input ViewChild is conditionally rendered so a setter is required to detect its activation.
setSignature.description: The input ViewChild is conditionally rendered so a setter is required to detect its activation.

components.templateData:
<select
  *ngIf="!showInput; else inputTemplate"
  (change)="selectChangeQuantity($event)"
  [disabled]="quantity.min === quantity.max"
  aria-label="quantity"
>
  <option value="" selected disabled hidden>
    {{ quantity.min }}
  </option>
  <option *ngFor="let option of quantity | quantityOptions">
    {{ option }}
  </option>
</select>
<ng-template #inputTemplate>
  <input
    aria-label="quantity"
    #input
    type="number"
    [step]="quantity.step"
    [formControl]="quantityFormControl"
  />
</ng-template>
<ov-button
  type="primary"
  (click)="submitQuantity()"
  ariaLabel="add to cart"
  [disabled]="!quantityFormControl.valid"
>
  <ov-icon icon="cart-plus" color="white" size="md"></ov-icon>
</ov-button>
